author: Doreen Christensen
title: Free lens cloth and cleaner at Walmart Vision Centers
text:
Free lens cloth and cleaner at Walmart Vision Centers Walmart Vision Centers offer free lens cleaner and cloth with a coupon. See a littler clearer with a free lens cloth and cleaner from Walmart. 
See things a little clearer with this freebie. 
Wal-Mart Vision Centers are offering a free lens cloth and bottle of cleaner for eye glasses with a coupon. 
No purchase is necessary. 
Print out the offer and bring it to a Vision Center, installed inside most Wal-Mart Supercenters. 
Click here for the deal. The offer is one per customer, while supplies last.
